{"type": "article", "id": 18431, "title": "工作喝酒两不误的桌子", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-03T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 149, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122414bPyIs4aR59vZCkfr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这张两用的桌子满足了白天工作晚上喝酒的愿望。白天工作的时候，是一张像钢琴一个的桌子，桌上有专门插电的凹槽。到了休息的时候就将桌子拉出，将后面可活动的挡板翻转过来形成一个台面，成为一个可以两边坐下来的酒吧。各类的酒就藏在挡板后，俨然是调酒师的空间。对合租者来说非常方便，售价 1375 美元，<a href=\"http://roundhead.design/collections/frontpage/products/convertible-desk\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122410oLqPQW7SrZbRxYaB.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83294118\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122411jH3knOIeKrdUEN8m.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83294118\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122412uMfRQgp6lysq7obX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122412TyF3k2x9Odso1KHl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122413gtX8WRuKq6Z7jBED.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83398438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122413CElNcsfLdqaGpVhS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}